9 AN ACT TO ENSURE THAT THE ARKANSAS MEDICAID PROGRAM
10 REIMBURSES FOR DENTAL AND ANESTHESIA COSTS FOR HIGH
11 COMPLEXITY ORAL HEALTH CARE; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
